<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٣٩٢ - تَلَا قَتَادَةُ <span class="c3">{فَمَا تَنْفَعُهُمْ شَفَاعَةُ الشَّافِعِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[المدثر: ٤٨]</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«يَعْلَمُونَ أَنَّ اللَّهَ يُشَفِّعُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ بَعْضُهُمْ فِي بَعْضٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>